fields.name: Conveyor jam

fields.name: Feeder misalignment
fields.description: Feeder not correctly seated or pickup error detected

fields.name: Wrong solder profile
fields.description: Incorrect reflow oven profile or temperature curve deviation

fields.description: Component not placed in its position during PNP process

fields.name: Solder paste dried

fields.name: AOI calibration drift
fields.description: Automatic Optical Inspection offset due to calibration drift

fields.description: Solder Paste Inspection threshold configured incorrectly

fields.name: Temperature variation
fields.description: Ambient temperature affecting solderability or machine vision
